&lt;p&gt;We are recognized as a Visionary in the Gartner Magic Quadrant for Analytics &amp;amp; Business Intelligence Platforms, and we&#39;re just getting started. Our team is built for people who thrive on solving hard problems, moving fast, and building things that matter at enterprise scale.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;
